            "title": "Protect, repair and strengthen a compromised skin barrier",
            "text": "<p>ENDOCARE AGE BARRIER provides targeted skincare solutions designed to strengthen barrier function and improve skin resilience. Ideal for patients experiencing dryness, sensitivity or a compromised skin barrier, AGE BARRIER complements both professional treatments and daily skincare routines.</p>",
